rows.label: qst202609_0010
rows.name: Ten'i... Are you all right?

rows.label: qst202609_0020
rows.name: Looks like we pulled the plug on rampage mode.

rows.label: qst202609_0030
rows.name: Smash my Core Crystal. It's...it's the only way.

rows.label: qst202609_0040
rows.name: Huh?!

rows.label: qst202609_0050
rows.name: This is the only chance you'll get...

rows.label: qst202609_0060
rows.name: The burden of my sin is already...too much to bear!

rows.label: qst202609_0070
rows.name: Shut the hell up!

rows.label: qst202609_0080
rows.name: We'd never do something like that, ever!

rows.label: qst202609_0090
rows.name: Then I will run rampant again...

rows.label: qst202609_0100
rows.name: and next time, innocents will suffer...

rows.label: qst202609_0110
rows.name: I don't want to hurt anyone any more...

rows.label: qst202609_0120
rows.name:
If you really care about me...
then please, end it...

rows.label: qst202609_0130
rows.name: Screw that!

rows.label: qst202609_0140
rows.name: I can't possibly agree to those terms either.

rows.label: qst202609_0150
rows.name: Why...?

rows.label: qst202609_0160
rows.name:
Don't you remember what King Serich
said? He entrusted you to us.

rows.label: qst202609_0170
rows.name: So that we would take care of you.

rows.label: qst202609_0180
rows.name:
Whether you go berserk or not,
it doesn't change a thing.

rows.label: qst202609_0190
rows.name:
Listen to Rex. The days of worrying about yourself
running out of control are over.

rows.label: qst202609_0200
rows.name: We'll stop you as many times as it takes.

rows.label: qst202609_0210
rows.name:
So don't ever think that you're better
off gone.

rows.label: qst202609_0220
rows.name:
You've already helped us so much.
Now we get to help you in return.

rows.label: qst202609_0230
rows.name: That's what friends are for, right?

rows.label: qst202609_0240
rows.name: Friends...

rows.label: qst202609_0250
rows.name: So, Ten'i? You get what we mean now?

rows.label: qst202609_0260
rows.name: So...you're saying you'd let me stay with you?

rows.label: qst202609_0270
rows.name: Need you even ask?

rows.label: qst202609_0280
rows.name: Thank you...
